{"tid":27333,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"［非跟風］我咁樣讀書定做野好","createTime":"2016-12-07T09:20:08.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-08T07:16:33.000Z","uid":59008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"315c4efb1a329b4c71d03876fbb8a89ee4fada06","tid":27333,"uid":59008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T09:20:08.000Z","msg":"是咁的小弟宜家廿歲有半 <br />\nHD岩岩完左sem1覺得自己真係唔岩讀書 雖然個科都叫ok有興趣<br />\n但係我一開始個心態已經係諗住捱過兩年就算<br />\n 返學為take attendance 功課又有遲交 test考天才波 <br />\n雖然叫仲差個exam未考<br />\n但係我覺得就算溫到好掂個gpa應該幾爛<br />\n<br />\n另外屋企個面又成日嘈 本身我就已經一早提老豆老母搞grant loan d野<br />\n一個就唔撚信人講野話邊洗咁多資料 一個個陣就發埋d細路脾氣名都唔肯簽<br />\n好啦 到而家下個sem準備要交學費先話唔夠錢 可唔可以宜家先去搞資助 哈真係搵撚野搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以宜家我係度諗既然佢地又話冇錢，我自己都唔知自己就算讀完兩年出黎係咪可以搵份人工ok既工<br />\n我到底應該quit搵工定係繼續讀書好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"055f0899c53d55365687ee39bf1823345084d09d","tid":27333,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T09:39:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n讀ive?<br />\n<br />\n讀左仲衰過未讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf7c861117182146921af43378b118b37806b50e","tid":27333,"uid":58666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T09:41:43.000Z","msg":"巴打讀咩科?"},{"pid":"59bfe20edfcac9a0da6eb1c587b0be99f5c1fcc7","tid":27333,"uid":59008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T09:46:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n讀ive?<br />\n<br />\n讀左仲衰過未讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係 我都唔知算唔算衰過冇讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb4a8c13aced96b129ddf2ac94a4e679e1cd824f","tid":27333,"uid":59008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12